###Exercises

>For each question below, answer which part of MCV should be responsible for it:

>A method that pulls the last 10 topics.

The Controller would pull this data for the client.

>A representation of the upvotes on a post.

The View would send this information to the client.

>Logic that parses params coming from the client.

The Model would contain these data structures.


>Write a user story with acceptance criteria for a feature that involves moderating content on Bloccit.

User Story: As a user with moderator credentials, I want to moderate content on Bloccit to ensure that off-topic or innapropriate content is filtered.

Acceptance Criteria:

While logged in and looking at a post, if the post is off-topic or innapropriate, I have the option to delete it.

